structure.unit: STOCK INSURANCE COMPANIES -- OTHER THAN LIFE (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 195, sec. 1, effective June 17, 1948. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 82, secs. 1 and 3. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 687, 762a-23.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Types of insurance that may be written by a company authorized to do other than life business.
